1937;;Madame X;;American;;Sam Wood;;Gladys George, Warren William, Reginald Owen;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madame_X_(1937_film);;A woman who cheated on her loving husband is thrown out of her home by said husband. Twenty years later, she finds herself accused of murder for saving her son, who does not know who she is as he was raised without her. He finds himself defending her without knowing her background.